track_notes: Hike up from the parking area on Rt 38 (N Shore Drive).
Obtained this route from Javi K6TNT.  Park at locked gate and hike the road the whole way to the top.  Rather steep and somewhat exposed to the sun, but a shorter route than form the south.
Would be a very easy hike if not for the elevation.  Very small parking area at trailhead, so you may need to park up the road.
